title: Supa Dupa Fly feat. Shounan no Kaze, Moomin, Kenty Gross, Bes, Apollo, Natural Weapon, Doraku

alternative_titles.ja: SUPA DUPA FLY feat. 湘南乃風, MOOMIN, KENTY GROSS, BES, APOLLO, NATURAL WEAPON, 導楽

synopsis: Official music video for Han-kun's song Supa Dupa Fly featuring Shounan no Kaze, Moomin, Kenty Gross, Bes, Apollo, Natural Weapon, Doraku in a massive ballad. It celebrates Han-kun's 10th anniversary as a hip-hop artist and the single will be available for sale the following day. The song's title is a homage to American rapper Missy Elliott's debut album of the same name from 1997.
